Thomas G. (Tom) Hartnett 

		
		President, Consumer Floral Brands, 

	
		 1-800-FLOWERS.COM, INC. 	

 
Last Updated: 03/06/2017 



Executive Summary
Thomas Hartnett has a background in accounting and experience across a wide range of disciplines, including retail, strategy, finance, and operations.  Hartnett worked as a CPA with Ernst & Young LLP from 1984 to 1991.  In 1991, he joined 1-800-FLOWERS.COM as Controller.  Harnett transitioned to store operations 
Current Focus

Enhancing the Customer Experience: “Our relentless focus on enhancing the customer experience and driving exemplary customer satisfaction metrics and our truly original product offerings from our signature Floral  
Biographical Highlights

Born c. 1963.
Hartnett was a certified public accountant with Ernst & Young LLP (1984-1991) 
 





